### Create Subscription - Yandex Plus
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_name": "Yandex Plus",
  "price": 400,
  "user_id": "60601fee-2bf1-4721-ae6f-7636e79a0cba",
  "start_date": "07-2025"
}

