### Get Subscriptions with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subscriptions?limit=2&offset=0

###

### Get Subscriptions by User ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subscriptions?user_id=60601fee-2bf1-4721-ae6f-7636e79a0cba

###

### Get Subscriptions by Service Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subscriptions?service_name=Netflix

###

### Get Subscriptions by Date Range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/subscriptions?start_date=01-2025&end_date=06-2025

###

### Get User Subscriptions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/60601fee-2bf1-4721-ae6f-7636e79a0cba/subscriptions

