### Calculate Total Cost for Period
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/costs/calculate?start_date=01-2025&end_date=12-2025

###

### Calculate Cost by User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/costs/calculate?user_id=60601fee-2bf1-4721-ae6f-7636e79a0cba&start_date=01-2025&end_date=12-2025

###

### Calculate Cost by Service
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/costs/calculate?service_name=Netflix&start_date=01-2025&end_date=12-2025

